\begin_layout Standard
The last operator used in our example is the 
\emph on
restriction
\emph default
 
\begin_inset listings
inline true
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
r.with(s)
\end_layout

\end_inset

 which is exactly the left-semijoin 
\begin_inset Formula $r\ltimes_{r.2=s.1}s$
\end_inset

,
 and it emulates SQL's 
\begin_inset listings
inline true
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout
WHERE
\end_layout

\end_inset

 clause.
